heif.boxes

Class FullBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • heif.boxes.Box
      • heif.boxes.FullBox
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuxiliaryTypePropertyBox, DataInformationBox.DataEntryBox, DataInformationBox.DataReferenceBox, HandlerBox, ImageSpatialExtentsProperty, ItemInformationBox, ItemInformationBox.ItemInfoEntry, ItemLocationBox, ItemPropertyAssociationBox, ItemProtectionBox, ItemReferenceBox, MetaBox, PixelInformationBox, PrimaryItemBox

    public class FullBox
extends Box
    This code creates a complete class that stores ubiquitous high-level data applicable for the majority of the derived Box objects, serving as the complete primary header box. It maintains details such as the entire size, including the size and type header, fields, and potentially contained boxes. This feature supports the parsing process of the HEIC file. For further technical details, refer to the Specification document - ISO/IEC 14496-12:2015 on Pages 6 and 7 under Object Structure.
    Since:
    13 August 2025
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Trevor Maggs
